<body>
    <h1>RFC: Query Explorer for DevQL</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"d5f84161c115" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-RFC:Q=
ueryExplorerforDevQL(DashboardImplementation)1.Summary">RFC: Query Explorer=
 for DevQL (Dashboard Implementation)<br><br>
1. Summary</h1>
<p local-id=3D"e65f56181f53">This RFC proposes the integration of a <strong=
>Query Explorer</strong> into our main dashboard. The goal is to provide en=
gineers with a GraphQL-inspired interface to interactively query repository=
 data. Under the hood, these queries are translated into <strong>DevQL</str=
ong> queries to pull deep insights about:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"29211c75-1629-4b95-b325-803ff51e87e5">
<li local-id=3D"2a21b89f-db68-4a43-91db-58b79f509914">
<p local-id=3D"77bf9b8b214d">Repositories and file structures</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"099e659b-35fa-4bb9-9324-9e9968c780ef">
<p local-id=3D"f36c1aca88d9">Code artefacts and their relationships</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"a5235b4e-1e95-45ba-a860-2173c4b4fd38">
<p local-id=3D"c79e13eb60ee">Semantic analysis and lineage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"17da30d2-0618-4f72-a4a5-f3402757d003">
<p local-id=3D"149dedb82d49">Behavioral telemetry</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"57cec399937c">The interface is designed for fast retrieval a=
nd is strictly <strong>read-only</strong>.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"ef36c5d7ec5b" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-2.Background"=
>2. Background</h2>
<p local-id=3D"f58f58fc9a41">Our existing dashboard is currently optimized =
for fixed views - primarily centered on specific checkpoints and commit his=
tory. While these views serve standard monitoring needs, developers often n=
eed to ask more nuanced questions that don't fit into a static UI.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6c0119895fd8"><strong>Common use cases include:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3bd2723a-2cf9-4c28-9d68-adc7b5ccac77">
<li local-id=3D"df25706e-dfd5-4be5-9645-aeb27cd40e08">
<p local-id=3D"37f381a7fb26">Pinpointing artefacts within narrow line range=
s.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ea7c6cf1-81a5-443a-b485-b1039a5bcbd3">
<p local-id=3D"2a365ff94351">Tracing dependencies and call relationships be=
tween functions.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3e9a57ba-996d-466d-865f-7f2638220efb">
<p local-id=3D"6130c8775e2b">Viewing semantic classifications.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"2cdbde78560f">Answering these today requires building custom=
 dashboard panels or manually running DevQL queries in an external environm=
ent. This Explorer will bridge that gap by allowing ad-hoc exploration dire=
ctly within the dashboard.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"d69755672d66" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-3.Goals">3. G=
oals</h2>
<p local-id=3D"fc851505693a">The Query Explorer is intended to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f36b2605-2ddc-4c16-9175-71da3c6b6eca">
<li local-id=3D"db057e1b-91e1-4935-8f33-d0d98a8e254f">
<p local-id=3D"90897adcf863">Provide a familiar, <strong>GraphQL-like</stro=
ng> syntax for querying.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a013021d-1d35-4d58-b0cb-d4df4100612c">
<p local-id=3D"7ac10950e05b">Support deep, nested traversal of repository e=
ntities.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"04997ab8-67ff-49ef-a76f-4ce2881cf013">
<p local-id=3D"e175cb885c41">Handle complex filtering via arguments and var=
iables.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"12486297-802e-4be3-8fb4-9bb0b82d4d11">
<p local-id=3D"d61fe00d9ce2">Deliver structured JSON results for easy inspe=
ction.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"43c901bf-c0f5-41c8-a8eb-01785f8043db">
<p local-id=3D"536ff7f565b7">Leverage <strong>schema-driven autocomplete</s=
trong> to aid query discovery.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"44dc480bd8e0">This will serve as a primary tool for develope=
rs exploring repository intelligence data, validating DevQL queries, debugg=
ing platform behavior and experimenting with new queries before they are ba=
ked into production tools.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"963a1a8801bf" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-4.Non-Goals">=
4. Non-Goals</h2>
<p local-id=3D"9ba0ed9331fa">This is not a full GraphQL implementation, so =
we are explicitly excluding:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a7c0d251-151d-4d9f-8570-b282bc851c3c">
<li local-id=3D"3d22c029-2ede-4473-9355-15998d3b16f9">
<p local-id=3D"a61f5d2c150e">GraphQL mutations, subscriptions, fragments an=
d directives.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"240a09e1-d889-4a18-a2e9-f1828ed6c05e">
<p local-id=3D"7d5dd0b044bd">Replacing DevQL (it remains our core execution=
 engine).</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"90b46342d01c" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-5.Proposal">5=
. Proposal</h2>
<p local-id=3D"527f810a96b6">We will introduce a dedicated <strong>Query Ex=
plorer mode</strong> in the dashboard. Users will be able to toggle between=
:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"d9e295ce-e129-4be1-928f-bf3d18f7aea0">
<li local-id=3D"591c3a1a-2bc2-48f0-9c98-79054c2d839b">
<p local-id=3D"8b0b20e9d73d"><strong>Dashboard Mode:</strong> Standard view=
s for commits and checkpoints.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5f8828a0-b283-43a2-9c1c-e45c3deaf1fc">
<p local-id=3D"fb91232ae3c8"><strong>Query Explorer Mode:</strong> An inter=
active IDE-style interface for custom queries.</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 local-id=3D"d7e3bdf0976a" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-6.Architectur=
e">6. Architecture</h2>
<p local-id=3D"bb026fbaa7d9">The query lifecycle follows a straightforward =
path:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"d8756a46-f860-4b57-82e4-cd64614b8cc8">
<li local-id=3D"319b83cd-ba6d-4aab-b18c-c7aa3ef21b20">
<p local-id=3D"0e71823df304"><strong>UI:</strong> User submits a query thro=
ugh the Explorer.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"52e907de-30cc-41a0-a60a-7c363ba36a8d">
<p local-id=3D"07ce4cdd644e"><strong>API:</strong> A <code>POST /query</cod=
e> request is sent to the backend.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2aba2a6c-d85e-4c60-9a75-25a2816339a9">
<p local-id=3D"fee5962e837e"><strong>Parsing/Validation:</strong> The backe=
nd parser validates the query against the schema.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a6a9735a-e69b-4b19-8da6-4b2861aa6052">
<p local-id=3D"220cc69d266f"><strong>Translation:</strong> Resolvers map th=
e nested GraphQL structure into a <strong>DevQL query</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f7079665-4e05-471c-b817-aa997e6bf34d">
<p local-id=3D"305a02aae577"><strong>Execution:</strong> The engine pulls d=
ata from the Relational Store (SQLite/Postgres), the Event Store (DuckDB / =
ClickHouse), and the Blob Store (local folder / GCP Cloud Storage / AWS S3)=
.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ebecf587-1d4f-4090-85c6-d52ebed4f6fb">
<p local-id=3D"53fe35fc7607"><strong>Response:</strong> Results are mapped =
back to the requested JSON structure and returned.</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 local-id=3D"257f0c1b7a77" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-7.QueryModel"=
>7. Query Model</h2>
<p local-id=3D"937c564d1bec">Queries utilise a tree structure that feels li=
ke standard GraphQL when queried in Declarative Graph Query (GraphQL-style)=
 mode.</p>
<p local-id=3D"2afc3a22a38e"><strong>Example Query:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">// DevQ=
L Declarative Graph Query (GraphQL-style)
query GetArtefacts($repo: String!, $ref: String!, $path: String!) {
  repo(name: $repo) {
    ref(name: $ref) {
      file(path: $path) {
        artefacts {
          symbolFqn
          canonicalKind
          semantics {
            summary
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"80467ae6e014"><strong>Equivalent DevQL Pipeline Query Mode:<=
/strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">// DevQ=
L (Pipeline Query Mode)
repo("repo1")
  -&gt; asOf(ref:"main")
  -&gt; file("src/auth/service.ts")
  -&gt; artefacts()
  -&gt; semantics()</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"d289c5b325f3" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-8.ConceptualS=
chema">8. Conceptual Schema</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3307c02459be">The schema is a direct reflection of our graph=
-based data model:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a7ed486e-76ab-4bfa-8249-6c13769cdc5d">
<li local-id=3D"c72d3c78-3a01-412d-8b0a-269a235fc831">
<p local-id=3D"592e9b942a02"><strong>Query Root:</strong> <code>repo(name)<=
/code>, <code>search(query)</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"025e8d2c-40b6-4c6d-95f7-71a6ff07ad61">
<p local-id=3D"412b6152af98"><strong>Repo:</strong> <code>ref(name)</code>,=
 <code>commit(sha)</code>, <code>files(path)</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"406700ce-aec7-47d2-a473-b20d04533855">
<p local-id=3D"380984583438"><strong>Ref:</strong> <code>file(path)</code>,=
 <code>files(path)</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e79de6b5-7d80-4182-babc-de1796ff8e3a">
<p local-id=3D"f277d3bbeaab"><strong>Artefact:</strong> <code>symbolFqn</co=
de>, <code>canonicalKind</code>, <code>semantics</code></p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"fbfca1921b5d" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-9.QueryExplor=
erUI">9. Query Explorer UI</h2>
<p local-id=3D"26127d9617c9">The interface will be split into three logical=
 panes:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">=E2=94=
=8C=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=
=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=
=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=
=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=
=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=
=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=90
=E2=94=82 Query Explorer                                =E2=94=82
=E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=
=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=
=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=
=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=
=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=
=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=A4
=E2=94=82 Query Editor              =E2=94=82 Result Viewer     =E2=94=82
=E2=94=82                           =E2=94=82                   =E2=94=82
=E2=94=82                           =E2=94=82                   =E2=94=82
=E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=
=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=
=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=
=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=B4=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=
=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=
=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=A4
=E2=94=82 Variables Panel                               =E2=94=82
=E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=
=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=
=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=
=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=
=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=
=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=80=E2=94=98</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"eba3f1514a19"><strong>Components:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"49f36f39-ae71-40ee-8dc1-304547fa87a7">
<li local-id=3D"f6ec0871-f7c3-4958-b0ea-5ed0beccbb51">
<p local-id=3D"d4adc138a53e"><strong>Query Editor:</strong> Supports syntax=
 highlighting, formatting.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aa00554f-66b5-4c52-ba4e-4283e344e836">
<p local-id=3D"deaa81838f52"><strong>Variables Panel:</strong> A dedicated =
space for dynamic parameters.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b4a76f8d-110e-454a-b541-ff93705a18cd">
<p local-id=3D"1b2bbfb4ec6d"><strong>Result Viewer:</strong> A collapsible =
JSON tree with inline error reporting for invalid fields or types.</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"3680ca3cb8e5" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-10.StateManag=
ement">10. State Management</h2>
<p local-id=3D"12187d6f4721">We will manage the explorer state locally to e=
nsure a snappy UI. Key states include the current query text, variables, lo=
ading status, and the autocomplete schema cache. We=E2=80=99ll look into pe=
rsisting query history and caching in future iterations.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"28c1c3669a34" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-11.Autocomple=
te">11. Autocomplete</h2>
<p local-id=3D"e84208cefdff">The Query Explorer supports <strong>schema-dri=
ven autocomplete</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c3e313abce07">Autocomplete suggestions are generated using:<=
/p>
<ul local-id=3D"20fbf27f-6c8d-4e82-8107-1ed314fc770a">
<li local-id=3D"4a46b386-6e92-4582-aa08-9795100eedf7">
<p local-id=3D"d4e7ea6bfb5e">query text</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"774e3ffe-1fdd-4bee-b42f-ca3ac03a9d90">
<p local-id=3D"184744fd42b6">cursor position</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"db09fc70-7dcf-43a1-a976-12ae54810d6e">
<p local-id=3D"4ddd8197a402">schema metadata</p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">Editor =
text + cursor
        =E2=86=93
Context resolver
        =E2=86=93
Schema metadata
        =E2=86=93
Autocomplete suggestions</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"22690921eb5d" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-BackendSchema=
Endpoint">Backend Schema Endpoint</h3>
<p local-id=3D"1b91fb5d737b">Example schema metadata response:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "Query": {
    "fields": {
      "repo": {
        "type": "Repo",
        "args": {
          "name": "String!"
        },
        "description": "Select a repository"
      }
    }
  },
  "Repo": {
    "fields": {
      "ref": {
        "type": "Ref",
        "args": {
          "name": "String!"
        }
      },
      "commit": {
        "type": "Commit",
        "args": {
          "sha": "String!"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"10282ba1e9e9">The frontend loads this schema and uses it to =
generate autocomplete suggestions.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8f1ea2f34fe8">Supported suggestions include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"bfde3485-e16c-4681-848e-3a2a143c915b">
<li local-id=3D"12b8d1fa-3e70-4bb2-bf32-ceb8f9bf091a">
<p local-id=3D"9386009aa2bf">root fields</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aff1066a-0d22-4c0c-be07-63bad054d6fb">
<p local-id=3D"fd2b452c0854">nested fields</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8ba47771-7235-4f49-80e6-2b0f8cf0aa0b">
<p local-id=3D"72a625e891d1">arguments</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a7e2afa5-cd00-4ee4-97c0-87cc426a2d20">
<p local-id=3D"876e597f8257">variables</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"6b1b4d039f9a" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-12.Validation=
">12. Validation</h2>
<p local-id=3D"f57a3fd24bf8">Validation occurs in both frontend and backend=
.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"825526aa8d56" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-Frontend">Fro=
ntend</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a4daf8303ead">Focuses on developer experience:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"0211b8e9-1a13-4f42-892c-3dac59322e50">
<li local-id=3D"21c6507b-4a5f-435f-9cd5-c2edce459ef6">
<p local-id=3D"d0061932577d">query cannot be empty</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4d898758-e8f7-42af-bfcf-e6ef0831c6d9">
<p local-id=3D"644127566c29">variables must contain valid JSON</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"da63e261-d7ed-4027-a2b4-0726cc7b785c">
<p local-id=3D"2c588200b08e">syntax highlighting and formatting</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"505dcb9ab3d0" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-Backend">Back=
end</h3>
<p local-id=3D"588702c11869">Responsible for authoritative validation:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"727bf597-f317-47f4-be34-9b7d3b59b0f6">
<li local-id=3D"40d9e32a-69b1-46ed-8af9-f0199a0beb6d">
<p local-id=3D"edfe08a200b4">schema correctness</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"771735d1-ebca-4188-bcd6-197a0000f3b2">
<p local-id=3D"56e9072eea3d">type enforcement</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cf084bbe-a749-44b4-97f6-e1e395c01091">
<p local-id=3D"3c5158976d59">argument validation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"643cb823-298f-4ae7-81d6-0c8c728e03f8">
<p local-id=3D"e8b64d51a656">query depth limits</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"35b8c029-6341-4851-a68d-9002c8786e89">
<p local-id=3D"fcb25d917dd9">execution limits</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b6611798-737d-4df6-b447-53bb0a4b5e34">
<p local-id=3D"4dd08bb2bfc9">DevQL compatibility</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"8955e9c34fdb" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-13.Alternativ=
esConsidered">13. Alternatives Considered</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"5016edcce60f" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-DashboardPane=
lsforEveryQuery">Dashboard Panels for Every Query</h3>
<p local-id=3D"c8ac158c14ac">Add UI panels for each data type.</p>
<p local-id=3D"76c87f26bfc9">Rejected because:</p>
<p local-id=3D"fffec8bb3589" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">- does not scal=
e</p>
<p local-id=3D"8e4a544b3112" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">- requires cons=
tant dashboard changes</p>
<p local-id=3D"ca1086baded0" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">- prevents ad h=
oc exploration</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"d86dd591efbc" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-DirectDevQLCo=
nsole">Direct DevQL Console</h3>
<p local-id=3D"d5c5a5397fd5">Expose DevQL directly to developers.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f96bc707a3f4">Rejected because:</p>
<p local-id=3D"0d73341fdce8">- DevQL syntax is less familiar<br>
- harder to validate client-side</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"82cdcd01da05" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-14.OpenQuesti=
ons">14. Open Questions</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"9200cd2c-a1ea-46dc-9de6-9dcfc4502fa1">
<li local-id=3D"95a1250c-61f8-4fac-9fd4-5da8b4053956">
<p local-id=3D"22511dfc36ba">Should query history be persisted locally?<br>
Yes, we can use the browser's local storage for local persistence, and we c=
an later move this to the backend and make an easy switch if we add the rig=
ht abstraction.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c58c52ef-7d3c-4618-a5bf-69919ee9723c">
<p local-id=3D"589d3a85042c">Should results support alternative visualisati=
ons (tree view /graph view)?<br>
Yes, but this is outside the current scope. We can start with a CodeCity gr=
aph when queried at an appropriate level.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"98d99bf4-5901-4f18-b35a-c8d25ebd6a33">
<p local-id=3D"63f348c42db6">Can we implement an "Open in Explorer" button =
from our existing commit views?<br>
Great idea, but outside the current scope.</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"ae355836e19c" id=3D"RFC:QueryExplorerforDevQL-15.Summary">1=
5. Summary</h2>
<p local-id=3D"c1aa9da1d5d0">This RFC introduces a Query Explorer embedded =
in the dashboard that enables developers to run GraphQL-like queries to ret=
rieve repository intelligence data.</p>
<p local-id=3D"2de9890f29bf">The system provides:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"512c29982553">
<li local-id=3D"e3af67dc92ee">
<p local-id=3D"d77d3d73c371">flexible exploration of repository intelligenc=
e</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6cdc6062eb4d">
<p local-id=3D"30f76f9b57ee">schema-driven autocomplete</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7604b02c6e47">
<p local-id=3D"80cf43f1be5b">structured JSON results</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a12a71e65e43">
<p local-id=3D"c16d1712098a">DevQL-powered execution</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"313e2ff28b90">This transforms the dashboard into a powerful =
developer exploration environment while preserving existing workflows.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
------=_Part_1484_52983440.1774266742317--
